text: Dr. Bibi Ameenah Firdaus Gurib-Fakim GCSK (born 17 October 1959) is a Mauritian politician and biodiversity scientist. She was the 6th President of Mauritius from 2015 to 2018. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Mauritius
title: Ameenah Gurib-Fakim
